## 🤝 Contributing

We welcome contributions from the community! Here's how you can help make V.A.U.L.T even better:

<div align="center">

### **🔄 Contribution Process**

```mermaid
graph LR
    A[🍴 Fork] --> B[🔧 Develop]
    B --> C[✅ Test]
    C --> D[📝 Document]
    D --> E[🚀 PR]
    E --> F[👀 Review]
    F --> G[🎉 Merge]
```

</div>

### **🛠️ Development Setup**

```bash
# Clone your fork
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/V.A.U.L.T.git
cd V.A.U.L.T

# Install development dependencies
pip install -r requirements-dev.txt

# Setup pre-commit hooks
pre-commit install

# Run tests
pytest tests/ -v --cov=vault

# Start development server
python -m vault.dev --hot-reload
```

### **📝 Contribution Guidelines**

<div align="center">

| Type | Description | Example |
|:----:|:------------|:--------|
| **🐛 Bug Fix** | Fix existing issues | `fix: resolve memory leak in ML pipeline` |
| **✨ Feature** | Add new functionality | `feat: add voice command support` |
| **📚 Docs** | Improve documentation | `docs: update API reference` |
| **🎨 Style** | Code formatting changes | `style: apply black formatting` |
| **♻️ Refactor** | Code restructuring | `refactor: optimize NLP processing` |

</div>

